#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:1
msgid "MoonBit Agent IDE"
msgstr "MoonBit Agent IDE"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:3
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "概览"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:5
msgid ""
"`moon ide` is a specialized CLI toolset for navigating, understanding, "
"and exploring MoonBit codebases. It provides semantic-aware tools for "
"code discovery using the compiler's knowledge of your project structure."
msgstr ""
"`moon ide` 是一套专门用于导航、理解和探索 MoonBit 代码库的 CLI 工具。它基于编译器对项目结构的理解，提供具备语义感知能力的代码发现工具。"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:7
msgid ""
"These commands use semantic analysis rather than text matching, making "
"them more precise than grep-based searching for code navigation tasks."
msgstr "这些命令使用语义分析而不是文本匹配，因此在代码导航任务中比基于 grep 的搜索更精确。"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:9
msgid "Available Commands"
msgstr "可用命令"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:11
msgid "**`moon ide peek-def`**: Locate symbol definitions with inline context"
msgstr "**`moon ide peek-def`**：在上下文中定位符号定义"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:12
msgid ""
"**`moon ide find-references`**: Locate all usages of a symbol across the "
"project"
msgstr "**`moon ide find-references`**：定位符号在整个项目中的所有用法"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:13
msgid "**`moon ide outline`**: Get a structural overview of files or packages"
msgstr "**`moon ide outline`**：获取文件或包的结构概览"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:14
msgid "**`moon ide doc`**: Discover and explore APIs with documentation"
msgstr "**`moon ide doc`**：结合文档发现并探索 API"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:16
msgid "Symbol Syntax"
msgstr "符号语法"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:18
msgid ""
"All `moon ide` subcommands accept a `<symbol>` argument using these "
"patterns:"
msgstr "所有 `moon ide` 子命令都接受 `<symbol>` 参数，支持以下模式："

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:20
msgid "**Basic symbols:**"
msgstr "**基础符号：**"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:22
msgid "`[@pkg.]symbol` - Symbol in a package (e.g. `parse_int`, `Array`)"
msgstr "`[@pkg.]symbol` - 包中的符号（例如 `parse_int`、`Array`）"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:23
msgid "If `@pkg.` is omitted, searches current package and prelude"
msgstr "如果省略 `@pkg.`，则搜索当前包和 prelude"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:25
msgid "**Type members:**"
msgstr "**类型成员：**"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:27
msgid ""
"`[@pkg.]Type::member` - Type methods, struct fields, enum variants, trait"
" methods"
msgstr "`[@pkg.]Type::member` - 类型方法、结构体字段、枚举变体、trait 方法"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:28
msgid "Examples: `Array::length`, `@http.Request::new`, `Option::None`"
msgstr "示例：`Array::length`、`@http.Request::new`、`Option::None`"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:30
msgid ""
"Package prefix `@pkg.` is optional for symbols in the current package and"
" standard library."
msgstr "对于当前包和标准库中的符号，包前缀 `@pkg.` 是可选的。"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:32
msgid "`moon ide peek-def` - View Symbol Definitions"
msgstr "`moon ide peek-def` - 查看符号定义"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:34
msgid ""
"Quickly locate symbol definitions with surrounding context. This is "
"faster and more precise than grepping for declarations."
msgstr "快速定位符号定义及其周边上下文。相比用 grep 查找声明，这种方式更快也更准确。"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:36 ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:82
#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:117 ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:164
msgid "Usage"
msgstr "用法"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:38
msgid "moon ide peek-def <symbol> [-loc filename:line[:col]]\n"
msgstr "moon ide peek-def <symbol> [-loc filename:line[:col]]\n"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:42
msgid "**Two modes:**"
msgstr "**两种模式：**"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:44
msgid ""
"**Global search** (no `-loc`): Searches the entire project using the "
"symbol syntax described above"
msgstr "**全局搜索**（不带 `-loc`）：使用上文描述的符号语法在整个项目中搜索"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:45
msgid ""
"**Contextual search** (`-loc` provided): Matches `<symbol>` as a "
"substring at the specified location"
msgstr "**上下文搜索**（提供 `-loc`）：在指定位置将 `<symbol>` 作为子串进行匹配"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:46
msgid "Line number must be precise; column is optional (used as a hint)"
msgstr "行号必须精确；列号可选（作为提示使用）"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:47
msgid ""
"The `<symbol>` argument is matched as plain text, not parsed as symbol "
"syntax"
msgstr "`<symbol>` 参数按纯文本匹配，不会按符号语法解析"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:48
msgid "Useful when a symbol name is ambiguous or appears in multiple contexts"
msgstr "当符号名有歧义或出现在多个上下文中时非常有用"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:50 ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:128
#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:200
msgid "Examples"
msgstr "示例"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:52
msgid ""
"$ moon ide peek-def Agent\n"
"Found 1 symbols matching 'Agent':\n"
"\n"
"`pub (all) struct Agent` in package moonbitlang/maria/agent at "
"./agent/agent.mbt:17-47\n"
"\n"
"17 | ///|\n"
"   | /// Represents an AI agent that interacts with language models and "
"executes tools.\n"
"...|\n"
"   | pub(all) struct Agent {\n"
"...|\n"
"...| }\n"
msgstr ""
"$ moon ide peek-def Agent\n"
"Found 1 symbols matching 'Agent':\n"
"\n"
"`pub (all) struct Agent` in package moonbitlang/maria/agent at "
"./agent/agent.mbt:17-47\n"
"\n"
"17 | ///|\n"
"   | /// Represents an AI agent that interacts with language models and "
"executes tools.\n"
"...|\n"
"   | pub(all) struct Agent {\n"
"...|\n"
"...| }\n"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:66
msgid ""
"$ moon ide peek-def Agent -loc ./maria.mbt:7\n"
"Definition found at file ./maria/agent/agent.mbt\n"
"   | ///\n"
"   | /// The `Agent` struct encapsulates the complete state and behavior "
"of an AI agent,\n"
"...|\n"
"24 | pub(all) struct Agent {\n"
"   |                 ^^^^^\n"
"   |   /// UUID generator for creating unique identifiers.\n"
"...|\n"
msgstr ""
"$ moon ide peek-def Agent -loc ./maria.mbt:7\n"
"Definition found at file ./maria/agent/agent.mbt\n"
"   | ///\n"
"   | /// The `Agent` struct encapsulates the complete state and behavior "
"of an AI agent,\n"
"...|\n"
"24 | pub(all) struct Agent {\n"
"   |                 ^^^^^\n"
"   |   /// UUID generator for creating unique identifiers.\n"
"...|\n"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:78
msgid "`moon ide find-references` - Track All Usages"
msgstr "`moon ide find-references` - 追踪所有用法"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:80
msgid "Discover where and how a symbol is used throughout your codebase."
msgstr "了解一个符号在整个代码库中的使用位置和方式。"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:84
msgid "moon ide find-references <symbol>\n"
msgstr "moon ide find-references <symbol>\n"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:88
msgid "Note: The `-loc` argument is not yet supported. Always searches globally."
msgstr "注意：目前还不支持 `-loc` 参数。始终执行全局搜索。"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:90
msgid "Example"
msgstr "示例"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:92
msgid ""
"$ moon ide find-references Agent\n"
"`pub (all) struct Agent` in package moonbitlang/maria/agent at "
"./agent/agent.mbt:17-47\n"
"17 | ///|\n"
"   | /// Represents an AI agent that interacts with language models and "
"executes tools.\n"
"...|\n"
"   | pub(all) struct Agent {\n"
"...|\n"
"...| }\n"
"Found 98 references of this symbol:\n"
"./agent/agent_tool.mbt:41:8-41:13:\n"
"   | /// * `agent` : The agent instance whose tools will be enabled or "
"disabled.\n"
"   | /// * `tool_names` : A set containing the names of tools that should"
" be enabled.\n"
"   | ///   Tools not in this set will be disabled.\n"
"41 | pub fn Agent::set_enabled_tools(\n"
"   |        ^^^^^\n"
"   |   agent : Agent,\n"
"   |   tool_names : Set[String],\n"
"...\n"
msgstr ""
"$ moon ide find-references Agent\n"
"`pub (all) struct Agent` in package moonbitlang/maria/agent at "
"./agent/agent.mbt:17-47\n"
"17 | ///|\n"
"   | /// Represents an AI agent that interacts with language models and "
"executes tools.\n"
"...|\n"
"   | pub(all) struct Agent {\n"
"...|\n"
"...| }\n"
"Found 98 references of this symbol:\n"
"./agent/agent_tool.mbt:41:8-41:13:\n"
"   | /// * `agent` : The agent instance whose tools will be enabled or "
"disabled.\n"
"   | /// * `tool_names` : A set containing the names of tools that should"
" be enabled.\n"
"   | ///   Tools not in this set will be disabled.\n"
"41 | pub fn Agent::set_enabled_tools(\n"
"   |        ^^^^^\n"
"   |   agent : Agent,\n"
"   |   tool_names : Set[String],\n"
"...\n"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:113
msgid "`moon ide outline` - Get Structural Overview"
msgstr "`moon ide outline` - 获取结构概览"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:115
msgid ""
"Quickly scan the structure of a file or package to understand its "
"organization."
msgstr "快速扫描文件或包的结构，理解其组织方式。"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:119
msgid "moon ide outline <path/to/file_or_directory>\n"
msgstr "moon ide outline <path/to/file_or_directory>\n"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:123
msgid "Two modes:"
msgstr "两种模式："

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:125
msgid "`moon ide outline path/to/file.mbt` - Outline a specific file"
msgstr "`moon ide outline path/to/file.mbt` - 查看单个文件的结构"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:126
msgid ""
"`moon ide outline path/to/directory` - Outline all `.mbt` files in the "
"package"
msgstr "`moon ide outline path/to/directory` - 查看包内所有 `.mbt` 文件的结构"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:130
msgid "**Package outline** - See all files and their top-level symbols:"
msgstr "**包结构** - 查看所有文件及其顶层符号："

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:132
msgid ""
"moon ide outline .\n"
"maria.mbt:\n"
" L05 | pub struct Maria {\n"
"       ...\n"
" L71 | pub fn Maria::close(self : Maria) -> Unit {\n"
"       ...\n"
" L84 | pub async fn Maria::start(self : Maria, prompt? : String) -> Unit "
"{\n"
msgstr ""
"moon ide outline .\n"
"maria.mbt:\n"
" L05 | pub struct Maria {\n"
"       ...\n"
" L71 | pub fn Maria::close(self : Maria) -> Unit {\n"
"       ...\n"
" L84 | pub async fn Maria::start(self : Maria, prompt? : String) -> Unit "
"{\n"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:142
msgid "**File outline** - Detailed view of a single file:"
msgstr "**文件结构** - 查看单个文件的详细结构："

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:144
msgid ""
"$ moon ide outline ./internal/readline/readline.mbt\n"
" L0002 | priv struct Edit {\n"
"         ...\n"
" L0008 | pub enum KeyName {\n"
"         ...\n"
" L0045 | pub struct Key {\n"
"         ...\n"
" L1369 | pub async fn Interface::start(self : Interface) -> Unit {\n"
"         ...\n"
" L1383 | pub async fn Interface::read_line(self : Interface) -> String {\n"
"         ...\n"
" L1390 | pub async fn Interface::read_key(self : Interface) -> Key {\n"
"         ...\n"
msgstr ""
"$ moon ide outline ./internal/readline/readline.mbt\n"
" L0002 | priv struct Edit {\n"
"         ...\n"
" L0008 | pub enum KeyName {\n"
"         ...\n"
" L0045 | pub struct Key {\n"
"         ...\n"
" L1369 | pub async fn Interface::start(self : Interface) -> Unit {\n"
"         ...\n"
" L1383 | pub async fn Interface::read_line(self : Interface) -> String {\n"
"         ...\n"
" L1390 | pub async fn Interface::read_key(self : Interface) -> Key {\n"
"         ...\n"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:160
msgid "`moon ide doc` - Discover and Explore APIs"
msgstr "`moon ide doc` - 发现与探索 API"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:162
msgid "Query documentation and discover available symbols, packages, and APIs."
msgstr "查询文档并发现可用的符号、包和 API。"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:166
msgid "moon ide doc '<query>'\n"
msgstr "moon ide doc '<query>'\n"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:170
msgid "Query Syntax"
msgstr "查询语法"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:172
msgid "The query syntax is specialized for symbol and package discovery:"
msgstr "查询语法专门用于符号和包的发现："

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:174
msgid "**Empty query** - List available packages or symbols:"
msgstr "**空查询** - 列出可用包或符号："

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:176
msgid "`moon ide doc ''`"
msgstr "`moon ide doc ''`"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:177
msgid ""
"In a module: Shows all available packages (including dependencies and "
"`moonbitlang/core`)"
msgstr "在模块内：显示所有可用包（包括依赖和 `moonbitlang/core`）"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:178
msgid "In a package: Shows all symbols in current package"
msgstr "在包内：显示当前包中的所有符号"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:179
msgid "Outside package: Shows all available packages"
msgstr "在包外：显示所有可用包"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:181
msgid "**Lookup by name:**"
msgstr "**按名称查找：**"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:183
msgid "`moon ide doc \"[@pkg.]function_name\"` - Find functions or values"
msgstr "`moon ide doc \"[@pkg.]function_name\"` - 查找函数或值"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:184
msgid ""
"`moon ide doc \"[@pkg.]TypeName\"` - Find types (builtin types don't need"
" prefix)"
msgstr "`moon ide doc \"[@pkg.]TypeName\"` - 查找类型（内建类型不需要前缀）"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:185 ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:187
msgid "`moon ide doc \"[@pkg.]Type::member\"` - Find type methods or fields"
msgstr "`moon ide doc \"[@pkg.]Type::member\"` - 查找类型方法或字段"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:189
msgid "**Package exploration:**"
msgstr "**包探索：**"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:191
msgid "`moon ide doc \"@pkg\"` - List all exported symbols in a package"
msgstr "`moon ide doc \"@pkg\"` - 列出一个包中所有导出符号"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:192
msgid "`moon ide doc \"@encoding/utf8\"` - Works with nested packages"
msgstr "`moon ide doc \"@encoding/utf8\"` - 支持嵌套包"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:193
msgid "Examples: `moon ide doc \"@json\"`, `moon ide doc \"@buffer\"`"
msgstr "示例：`moon ide doc \"@json\"`、`moon ide doc \"@buffer\"`"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:195
msgid "**Globbing** - Use `*` wildcard for partial matches:"
msgstr "**通配匹配（Globbing）** - 使用 `*` 通配符进行部分匹配："

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:197
msgid ""
"`moon ide doc \"String::*rev*\"` - Find all String methods containing "
"\"rev\""
msgstr "`moon ide doc \"String::*rev*\"` - 查找名称中包含 \"rev\" 的所有 String 方法"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:198
msgid "`moon ide doc \"*parse*\"` - Find all symbols with \"parse\" in the name"
msgstr "`moon ide doc \"*parse*\"` - 查找名称中包含 \"parse\" 的所有符号"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:202
msgid "**Search for type methods:**"
msgstr "**搜索类型方法：**"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:204
msgid ""
"# Search for String methods in standard library:\n"
"$ moon ide doc \"String\"\n"
"\n"
"type String\n"
"\n"
"  pub fn String::add(String, String) -> String\n"
"  # ... more methods omitted ...\n"
msgstr ""
"# Search for String methods in standard library:\n"
"$ moon ide doc \"String\"\n"
"\n"
"type String\n"
"\n"
"  pub fn String::add(String, String) -> String\n"
"  # ... more methods omitted ...\n"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:214
msgid "**Explore a package:**"
msgstr "**探索一个包：**"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:216
msgid ""
"$ moon ide doc \"@buffer\"\n"
"moonbitlang/core/buffer\n"
"\n"
"fn from_array(ArrayView[Byte]) -> Buffer\n"
"# ... omitted ...\n"
msgstr ""
"$ moon ide doc \"@buffer\"\n"
"moonbitlang/core/buffer\n"
"\n"
"fn from_array(ArrayView[Byte]) -> Buffer\n"
"# ... omitted ...\n"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:224
msgid "**Query a specific function:**"
msgstr "**查询特定函数：**"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:226
msgid ""
"$ moon ide doc \"@buffer.new\"\n"
"package \"moonbitlang/core/buffer\"\n"
"\n"
"pub fn new(size_hint? : Int) -> Buffer\n"
"  Creates ... omitted ...\n"
msgstr ""
"$ moon ide doc \"@buffer.new\"\n"
"package \"moonbitlang/core/buffer\"\n"
"\n"
"pub fn new(size_hint? : Int) -> Buffer\n"
"  Creates ... omitted ...\n"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:234
msgid "**Use globbing to find related functions:**"
msgstr "**使用通配匹配查找相关函数：**"

#: ../../toolchain/moonide/index.md:236
msgid ""
"$ moon ide doc \"String::*rev*\"\n"
"package \"moonbitlang/core/string\"\n"
"\n"
"pub fn String::rev(String) -> String\n"
"  Returns ... omitted ...\n"
"  # ... more\n"
"\n"
"pub fn String::rev_find(String, StringView) -> Int?\n"
"  Returns ... omitted ...\n"
msgstr ""
"$ moon ide doc \"String::*rev*\"\n"
"package \"moonbitlang/core/string\"\n"
"\n"
"pub fn String::rev(String) -> String\n"
"  Returns ... omitted ...\n"
"  # ... more\n"
"\n"
"pub fn String::rev_find(String, StringView) -> Int?\n"
"  Returns ... omitted ...\n"
